show.title: Divine Doctor Son-In-Law
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/xkupK3
show.description: Sam, a chronically ill patient, had a dream that changed his fate. In his sleep, he watches his wife betray him with another man. Powerless to stop them, he’s beaten and broken—even in his dream. But when he wakes up, something inside him has changed. A mysterious power now flows through him.  And this time, he's not the one who’ll suffer.
